{"tid":2441240,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"【豆腐渣】礦工已破解 NVIDIA 挖礦限制GeForce RTX 3060 算力重返 45 MH/s","createTime":"2021-03-10T13:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T17:11:35.000Z","uid":15564,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1d1949bd664e97bffe0a6c8a7925f30dad59a784","tid":2441240,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:57:50.000Z","msg":"NVIDIA 為了冷卻顯示卡挖礦市場，在剛上市的 GeForce RTX 3060 顯示卡中加入「偵測挖礦算法限制」，偵測到掘礦動作時會直接 hashrate 算力減 50%，藉此希望能為遊戲玩家提供穩定的顯示卡供貨，傳聞 4 月上市的 GeForce RTX 3080 Ti 亦會採用相同做法，可惜不足一個月已被礦工們完美破解了，RTX3060 / RTX 3080 Ti 想便宜就難了。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n據了解，GeForce RTX 3060 算力限制是基於 GPU、驅動程式與 VBIOS 三者之間的握手動作，當偵測到用家進行 Hash 運算時會強迫 GPU 運算降速，NVIDIA 原本對這個限制充滿信心，沒想到不足一個月已被完美破解，據知是透過修過 VBIOS 及驅動程式允許礦工再次繞過限制。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nNVIDIA GeForce RTX 3060 初推出時，使用 Dagger Hashi-Motto 算法大約只有 22~23 MH/s，速度與舊有 GeForce GTX 1060 相約，但換上了被破解的 VBIOS 及 驅動程式後，GeForce RTX 3060 的算力被完全釋放重上 45MH/s，圖中的系統正使用 8 張 GeForce RTX 3060，其 Hashrate 可達 362.75MH/s 相當可觀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2021/03/source/10181536361342047856.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2021%2F03%2Fsource%2F10181536361342047856.jpeg&h=b098644d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/20162/%E8%B1%86%E8%85%90%E6%B8%A3%E7%A4%A6%E5%B7%A5%E5%B7%B2%E7%A0%B4%E8%A7%A3_NVIDIA_%E6%8C%96%E7%A4%A6%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6_GeForce_RTX_3060_%E7%AE%97%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8D%E8%BF%94_45_MHs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F20162%2F%25E8%25B1%2586%25E8%2585%2590%25E6%25B8%25A3%25E7%25A4%25A6%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E8%25A7%25A3_NVIDIA_%25E6%258C%2596%25E7%25A4%25A6%25E9%2599%2590%25E5%2588%25B6_GeForce_RTX_3060_%25E7%25AE%2597%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25BF%2594_45_MHs&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=b0fad0ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/20162/%E8%B1%86%E8%85%90%E6%B8%A3%E7%A4%A6%E5%B7%A5%E5%B7%B2%E7%A0%B4%E8%A7%A3_NVIDIA_%E6%8C%96%E7%A4%A6%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6_GeForce_RTX_3060_%E7%AE%97%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8D%E8%BF%94_45_MHs</a>"},{"pid":"71e4123bd36bda774ab1c3e9f5bee349687066c1","tid":2441240,"uid":22054,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"根本就on9，軟鎖實解到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f932f642fef55ed848038f6eccaeb64c79ba88d6","tid":2441240,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T14:01:10.000Z","msg":"哈希就哈希啦<br />\nhash 咩阿"},{"pid":"279af2de7ce4b7495a63517f6fbf7b19f5274b20","tid":2441240,"uid":79510,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T14:02:36.000Z","msg":"所以cmp根本係開多條生產線供比礦佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da838f16ed42fff1f10fbce28df7ab4d4b2263d","tid":2441240,"uid":67346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f932f642fef55ed848038f6eccaeb64c79ba88d6","tid":2441240,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T14:01:10.000Z","msg":"哈希就哈希啦<br />\nhash 咩阿"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T14:04:35.000Z","msg":"牛逼死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796d234c3ffd622eb04863c6995d16f277303a3c","tid":2441240,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5da838f16ed42fff1f10fbce28df7ab4d4b2263d","tid":2441240,"uid":67346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f932f642fef55ed848038f6eccaeb64c79ba88d6","tid":2441240,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T14:01:10.000Z","msg":"哈希就哈希啦<br />\nhash 咩阿"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T14:04:35.000Z","msg":"牛逼死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T14:06:44.000Z","msg":"點解死咗<br />\n英年早逝好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ecca4555767616df5f50218714